ante oculos mentis domū ędifi¬ care in m̅sas moles leuare pen¬ dere <note>Strich über e</note> magnas in machinis colum¬ nas qͥs quęso te hoc opus operat corpus uisibile qđ illas moles manib trahit an inuisibilis anima quę uiuificat corpus #Tolle enī qđ n̅ uidet in corpore et mox inmobilia remanent cuncta quę moueri uidebant uisibilia corporea metallorū #Qua in re pensandū e̅ quia in hoc quoq mundo uisibili nihil nisi ꝑ creaturā inuisibilē disponi potest Nā sicut om̅ps ds̅ asspi¬ rando ꝉ implendo ea quę rati¬ one subsistunt et uiuificat et mouet inuisibilia ita ipsa qͦq inuisibilia implendo mouent atq sensim uiuificant carnalia corpora quę uident PETRVS #Istis fateor allegationib libent̅ uictus ꝓpe nulla iā ee̅ hęc uisibilia conpellor existimare qui prius in me infirmantium ꝑsonas suscipiens de inuisibilib dubitabā Itaq placent cuncta quę dicis sed tam̅ sicut uitā animę in corpore manentis ex motu corporis agnosco ita
sp̅s tenet in corpore cur n̅ post
mortē cū in corporeus sit sp̅s etiā
poreus sp̅s tenet in corpore qͥa
possit et ibi teneri ubi a corporeo
~Si in corporeus sp̅s petre in hoc
teneri potest qđ uiuificat qᷓ re
n̅ penalit̅ et ibi teneat ubi morti¬

in corporeā exurat dū ex igne
mens in corporea etiā in corpo¬

uitā animę post corpus aꝑtis quibusdā rebus attestantibus agnoscere cupio *86*Qđ in corporeus sp̅s in inferno a corporeo igne affligatur ~Si uiuentis hominis in corporeus sp̅s tenet in corpore cur n̅ post mortē cū in corporeus sit sp̅s etiā corporeo igne teneat PETRVS #In uiuente quolibet idcirco in cor¬ poreus sp̅s tenet in corpore qͥa uiuificat corpus *87*Qđ in corporeus sp̅s uiuificare possit et ibi teneri ubi a corporeo cruciatur igni ~Si in corporeus sp̅s petre in hoc teneri potest qđ uiuificat qᷓ re n̅ penalit̅ et ibi teneat ubi morti¬ ficat Teneri autē ꝑ ignē sp̅m hominis dicimus ut in torm̅to ignis sit uidendo atq sentiendo #Ignē nāq eo ipso patit quo uidet et quia concremari se aspicit cremat Sicq fit ut res corporea in corporeā exurat dū ex igne uisibili ardor ac dolor inuisibilis trahit ut ꝑ ignē corporeum mens in corporea etiā in corpo¬ rea flāma cruciet Quāuis colli¬ gere dictis euangelicis possumus
